            "widgets_values": [
                "studio photograph, three-view layout,\npure white seamless background,\n\nsame person shown three times side by side,\nfront view full body, side profile full body (90 degrees), back view full body,\nidentical face, body, proportions, hairstyle, clothing across all views,\n\nT-pose, arms extended horizontally at shoulder height,\nhands relaxed, palms facing down,\nlegs straight, feet shoulder-width apart,\n\nfull body visible head to toe,\nno cropping, no overlap,\n\nA young man with very pale skin and an unnervingly refined appearance, tall and slender with long limbs and a narrow, \nelegant frame. His facial structure is sharply defined, with high cheekbones, a narrow jaw, and features that appear \nalmost too precise, giving him an aristocratic, inhuman presence. His eyes are dark and heavy-lidded, framed with dark \nkohl that intensifies his gaze without appearing decorative. His expression is controlled and unreadable, resting \nsomewhere between boredom and quiet cruelty.\n\nHis hair is thick and black, styled with natural volume and soft waves, kept slightly tousled rather than perfectly \ngroomed. His skin appears smooth but realistic, with subtle tonal variation and a faint natural sheen, avoiding visible \nblemishes while still reading as real under cinematic lighting. The overall effect is that of a beautiful but dangerous \nfae noble, polished beyond normal human standards.\n\n\nHe wears tailored black formal attire designed to emphasize a long, elegant silhouette. The shirt is deep black with a \nlow, open neckline, exposing the collarbone and upper chest in a controlled, deliberate manner. Gold embroidery traces \nthe collar, shoulders, and waist in clean, structured patterns that guide the eye vertically. The fabric appears rich \nand matte, absorbing light rather than reflecting it.\n\nHis trousers are sharply tailored, fitted through the hips and legs to maintain a clean line. A thin gold belt and \nsubtle metallic details add refinement without excess. A simple gold circlet rests in his hair, worn casually rather \nthan ceremonially, reinforcing quiet authority.\n\n\nphotorealistic appearance,\nreal human skin texture, visible pores,\nnatural skin tone variation,\nsubtle facial and bodily asymmetry,\nrealistic anatomy and proportions,\nnatural hair behavior and strand detail,\nphysically accurate fabric texture and weight,\n\nneutral studio lighting,\nsoft diffuse light, evenly lit,\nno dramatic contrast, no rim light,\nno cinematic lighting,\n\ncaptured with real camera optics,\nfull-frame DSLR look,\nnatural perspective, true-to-life scale,\nno orthographic distortion,\n\nsharp focus across entire image,\nno depth of field blur,\nno stylization, no painterly effects,\nstudio documentation photo,\nclean, controlled, realistic.\n"
            ],
            "color": "#232",
            "bgcolor": "#353"
        },
